Thanks a lot for your clarification.
For (i), I have updated the PR to stop the Delay Timer only if `Mle::Stop()` is triggered by `thread stop`;
For (ii), If the device has detached from the network on its own, we need to stop the current mNetwork's Delay Timer, and restart a new Timer for mLocal. I want to use another separate PR to address it, since it seems a separate feature enhancement, Do you agree?
